[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/captivate">Captivate</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/captivate">Captivate</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>If it is the opposite gender of the user, the foe is charmed into sharply lowering its SpA stat.</p>